# Smart Military Tank

## Overview
A Smart Military Tank prototype developed using IoT and embedded systems for defense and surveillance applications.

## Features
- Ultrasonic-based object detection
- Missile firing mechanism
- Emergency fire alarm system
- Built-in mini drone deployment
- Mine-removal attachment
- Chained wheels for better terrain grip

## Components Used
- Arduino Uno
- Ultrasonic Sensor
- Servo Motors
- DC Motors
- L298N Motor Driver
- Buzzer
- Battery Pack

## Technologies
- Arduino C++
- IoT
- Robotics
- Embedded Systems
